      <title>centos7 yum安装MySQL5.6</title>
      <link href="2020/11/23/mysql-1/"/>
      <url>2020/11/23/mysql-1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li>下载wget包管理工具</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell">yum <span class="hljs-literal">-y</span> install <span class="hljs-built_in"><code class="language-hljs powershell">yum <span class="hljs-literal">-y</span> install <span class="hljs-built_in">wget</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="2"><li>下载mysql的rpm包</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell"><span class="hljs-built_in">wget</span> http://repo.mysql.com/mysql<span class="hljs-literal">-community</span><span class="hljs-literal">-release</span><span class="hljs-literal">-el7</span><span class="hljs-literal"><code class="language-hljs powershell"><span class="hljs-built_in">wget</span> http://repo.mysql.com/mysql<span class="hljs-literal">-community</span><span class="hljs-literal">-release</span><span class="hljs-literal">-el7</span><span class="hljs-literal">-5</span>.noarch.rpm<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="3"><li>解压rpm包</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell">rpm <span class="hljs-literal">-ivh</span> mysql<span class="hljs-literal">-community</span><span class="hljs-literal">-release</span><span class="hljs-literal">-el7</span><span class="hljs-literal"><code class="language-hljs powershell">rpm <span class="hljs-literal">-ivh</span> mysql<span class="hljs-literal">-community</span><span class="hljs-literal">-release</span><span class="hljs-literal">-el7</span><span class="hljs-literal">-5</span>.noarch.rpm<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="4"><li>安装mysql服务</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell">yum <span class="hljs-literal">-y</span> install mysql<span class="hljs-literal"><code class="language-hljs powershell">yum <span class="hljs-literal">-y</span> install mysql<span class="hljs-literal">-server</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="5"><li>启动mysql，开机自启</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell">systemctl <span class="hljs-built_in"><code class="language-hljs powershell">systemctl <span class="hljs-built_in">start</span> mysqldsystemctl enable mysqld<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="6"><li>登录mysql</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell"><code class="language-hljs powershell">mysql<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="7"><li>修改密码</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell"><span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> password <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> root@localhost = password(<span class="hljs-string"><code class="language-hljs powershell"><span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> password <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> root@localhost = password(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>);<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="8"><li>开放远程连接</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-hljs powershell">grant all privileges on *.* to <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-string"><code class="language-hljs powershell">grant all privileges on *.* to <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;root&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-string">@&#x27;%&#x27; identified by &#x27;root&#x27; with grant option;</span><span class="hljs-string">flush privileges;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
